gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 144, Clippers 126
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks defeated the Clippers, 144-126. Luka Doncic recorded a game high 44 points, along with six rebounds and six assists for the Mavericks, with Kyrie Irving adding 27 points, six rebounds, and three assists in the victory. Kawhi Leonard tallied 26 points, four assists, and three rebounds for the Clippers in the losing effort. The Mavericks improve to 1-1 in West Group B play, and 7-2 in the regular season, while the Clippers fall to 0-1 in West Group B play, and 3-5 in the regular season.
